									<a rel="nofollow" class="cat-post-thumbnail  cat-post-none" href="https://journalistsresource.org/studies/economics/consumer-spending-coronavirus-pandemic/" rel="bookmark" title="Economic earthquake: Consumer spending in the wake of the coronavirus pandemic">
										<span class="rthumb">
																							<img width="75" height="75" src="https://journalistsresource.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/kelly-sikkema-kp7ENPlp8no-unsplash-75x75.jpg" class="attachment-sidethumb size-sidethumb wp-post-image" alt="" title="" srcset="https://journalistsresource.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/kelly-sikkema-kp7ENPlp8no-unsplash-75x75.jpg 75w, https://journalistsresource.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/kelly-sikkema-kp7ENPlp8no-unsplash-150x150.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 75px) 100vw, 75px" />																					</span>
